org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.files

Class FileBasedLock

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.files.FileBasedLock

  • public class FileBasedLock
extends java.lang.Object
    FileBasedLock provides non-recursive exclusive-lock semeantics across threads and across processes by means of file-system artifacts: a directory, files, and timestamps. Recovery for crashed processes is provided.
